{"tid":416350,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"關於港獨,有一個好嚴重既問題","createTime":"2017-09-27T16:47:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-08T15:06:21.000Z","uid":119994,"like":1,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"1c7c8c47c8a8dad10bd65baab4117b2c21a93141","tid":416350,"uid":119994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T16:47:07.000Z","msg":"成日話「香港獨立」「獨立」<br />\n但都無認真諗過咩叫做「獨立」<br />\n岩岩查字典，獨立係解「是與依賴、依附相反的狀態」<br />\n講「香港獨立」，無疑係認同左現時香港於鬼國既統治下<br />\n於爭取自主既同時，我地會確立緊鬼國既地位<br />\n所以咁多位巴打，有無諗過我地要正名？<br />\n係唔加強蝗國既政治正當性既情況下，爭取真正既港人治港？"},{"pid":"8ab09ad222d0749a721b046ed2c5775a3846e4ed","tid":416350,"uid":48579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T16:53:29.000Z","msg":"其實我唔知你想講乜"},{"pid":"f7c361c50ee64957baabdec2df8f22743d7fc6b0","tid":416350,"uid":92301,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T16:54:10.000Z","msg":"立國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3146d161b39743af7c714f63d205392c46707cc7","tid":416350,"uid":169,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T16:55:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"73d61d32b21415698736719018ec2f9621fb6748","tid":416350,"uid":73945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T16:56:21.000Z","msg":"係唔係得我睇唔明佢up乜9"},{"pid":"45f409b05882ab8fe1081b97a2876e6ad355c874","tid":416350,"uid":9119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T16:56:28.000Z","msg":"建國"},{"pid":"1372de07c80d14d818665499883cf62762f2119b","tid":416350,"uid":14476,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T16:58:54.000Z","msg":"香港嘅光芒就係佢係中國獨特一部分，而香港可以令佢地更方便進入中國市場或中國走資嘅一個橋樑，唔中意都講返句，獨立左根本會更邊緣化，無晒利用價值。"},{"pid":"1e34e6f32fd7a132c61bbf1b4ed6d9a5d893c8d4","tid":416350,"uid":70359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T18:07:36.000Z","msg":"香港建國"},{"pid":"ea1d7a6b9e212a08890fad84a4d8283d8e2947b9","tid":416350,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"